00:46:34.730 --> 00:46:36.320
that we are aware of.

00:46:36.320 --> 00:46:39.220
So I guess, navigating
through this world,

00:46:39.220 --> 00:46:42.460
I obviously am not condoning
that we should change

00:46:42.460 --> 00:46:43.460
