00:47:06.370 --> 00:47:07.850
you've tried as like a leader?

00:47:07.850 --> 00:47:08.760
WENDY SACHS: Yeah.

00:47:08.760 --> 00:47:11.540
Yeah, I do think that a lot
of it is facial expression.

00:47:11.540 --> 00:47:14.110
So the problem when I was
told that I was abrasive,

00:47:14.110 --> 00:47:16.020
I was actually working remotely.

00:47:16.020 --> 00:47:18.560
So a lot of my conversations
were over the phone.

00:47:18.560 --> 00:47:20.430
So I thought I was
being very direct.

00:47:20.430 --> 00:47:23.140
And my boss actually said
to me, who is a woman,

00:47:23.140 --> 00:47:25.240
she said, I know
that you're warm.

00:47:25.240 --> 00:47:28.160
You smile, you're very
engaging in person.

00:47:28.160 --> 00:47:29.810
But you know, on
the phone, people

00:47:29.810 --> 00:47:32.050
think you're a little bossy.

00:47:32.050 --> 00:47:33.940
And again, a man
would never have

00:47:33.940 --> 00:47:35.540
been accused of being bossy.

00:47:35.540 --> 00:47:36.800
I was just direct.

00:47:36.800 --> 00:47:38.510
I thought, we've got time.

00:47:38.510 --> 00:47:41.810
We've got 30 minutes on the
call, in, out, done, good.

00:47:41.810 --> 00:47:46.520
